# Meili-AI (MerYDiaN) ‚Äî Frontend Architecture Guide

> **Framework**: Next.js 15 (App Router) ¬∑ **Styling**: Tailwind CSS ¬∑ **State**: React Context (AuthContext)  
> **Root**: `frontend/`

---

## 1. High-Level Folder Structure

```
frontend/
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ app/                    # Next.js App Router ‚Äî all routes live here
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ layout.tsx          # Root layout (fonts, AuthProvider wrapper)
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ page.tsx            # "/" landing page
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ globals.css         # Global styles
‚îÇ   ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ [route-dirs]/       # Each directory = a URL route
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ components/             # Shared, reusable components (non-route)
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ landing/            # Landing page sections
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ itinerary/          # Itinerary views used by agent & customer
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ charts/             # Chart components (Intelligence page)
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ chat/               # AgentChatPanel
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ common/             # Navigation, breadcrumbs, progress bars
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ ui/                 # Generic UI primitives (Sidebar, AppIcon, etc.)
‚îÇ   ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ demo/               # Demo dashboard components
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ contexts/               # React Contexts
‚îÇ   ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ AuthContext.tsx      # Auth state, login/signup/logout, JWT decode
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ services/               # API & backend service clients
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ api.ts              # Core API client (login, signup, refresh, CRUD)
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ itinerary.service.ts
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ map.service.ts
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ media.service.ts
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ poi.service.ts
‚îÇ   ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ websocket.service.ts
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ hooks/                  # Custom React hooks
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ lib/                    # Utilities, data files, helper functions
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ types/                  # TypeScript type definitions
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ sockets/                # WebSocket configuration
‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ public/                 # Static assets (images, icons, frames)
```

