## 2. Root Layout & Auth Flow

### [layout.tsx](file:///c:/Users/Lenovo/OneDrive/Desktop/Coding/Projects/Meili-AI/Meili-AI/frontend/app/layout.tsx)

Every page is wrapped by:
```
<AuthProvider>     ‚Üê from contexts/AuthContext.tsx
  {children}       ‚Üê route pages
</AuthProvider>
```

### Auth Redirect Rules (in [AuthContext.tsx](file:///c:/Users/Lenovo/OneDrive/Desktop/Coding/Projects/Meili-AI/Meili-AI/frontend/contexts/AuthContext.tsx))

| Action | Agent Role | Customer (Traveller) Role |
|--------|-----------|--------------------------|
| After **login** | ‚Üí `/agent-dashboard` | ‚Üí `/customer-portal` |
| After **signup** | ‚Üí `/agent-dashboard` | ‚Üí `/customer-portal` |
| After **logout** | ‚Üí `/login` | ‚Üí `/login` |

