## 6. Key Navigation Flows

### Customer Journey
```
Landing (/) 
  ‚Üí Sign Up (/signup) or Customer Login (/customer-login)
    ‚Üí Customer Portal (/customer-portal)
      ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ View Trips ‚Üí Itinerary (/customer-itinerary/[tripId])
      ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Plan New Trip ‚Üí Itinerary Selection (/itinerary-selection)
      ‚îÇ     ‚Üí Trip Request Form (/customer-trip-request)
      ‚îÇ       ‚Üí Itinerary Review (/customer-itinerary-view)
      ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ View Bookings (/customer-bookings)
      ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Set Preferences (/customer-preference)
      ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ Trip Detail with Chat (/trip/[id])
```

### Agent Journey
```
Landing (/) 
  ‚Üí Agent Login (/agent-login)
    ‚Üí Itinerary Management (/agent-dashboard/itinerary-management)
      ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Create New Trip (/agent-dashboard/itinerary-management/new)
      ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Select Trip ‚Üí Trip Detail (‚Ä¶/[tripId])
      ‚îÇ     ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Tab: Itinerary (‚Ä¶/[tripId])
      ‚îÇ     ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Tab: Bookings (‚Ä¶/[tripId]/bookings)
      ‚îÇ     ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Tab: Groups (‚Ä¶/[tripId]/groups)
      ‚îÇ     ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ Tab: Intelligence (‚Ä¶/[tripId]/intelligence)
      ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ Itinerary Builder (/agent-dashboard/itinerary-builder)
    ‚Üí Review Customer Requests (/agent-request-review)
    ‚Üí Itinerary Editor (/optimizer)
    ‚Üí Analytics (/analytics)
```

